{"tid":1758561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊將資助被起底警員換車牌","createTime":"2019-11-27T06:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T12:54:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":522,"uniUserReply":136,"replies":[{"pid":"0dfd0ef2ea3c4ead85db54ce98ff63b83a5a510b","tid":1758561,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:28:46.000Z","msg":"消息指，警方決定資助被「起底」的警務人員更換車牌，今天起接受申請。<br />\n<br />\n警方人事部發出通知，指鑑於有不少警員被「起底」，包括車牌號碼在不同公眾平台被公開，對警務人員及車輛安全造成潛在風險。<br />\n<br />\n警隊管理層決定以警察福利基金，資助受影響人員更換新車牌及新造車牌的開支，包括560元行政費及最多300元買新車牌，今天起接受申請，申請資格必須是車牌被起底的現職警務人員，每人可獲一次資助。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1647604/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%B0%87%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E8%A2%AB%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%9B%E8%BB%8A%E7%89%8C-%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B</code></pre>"},{"pid":"9cd87626ed1002f2073143cdc364b29203ec57e1","tid":1758561,"uid":4780,"like":378,"dislike":1,"score":377,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:29:49.000Z","msg":"唔爭在資助埋換樓啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ad27a7f10d98786d609356fff8509b8b2ed2bc","tid":1758561,"uid":196924,"like":171,"dislike":1,"score":170,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:30:35.000Z","msg":"幾舊水都sponsor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e38355ad36a8e42724507ee26990b075bcd832","tid":1758561,"uid":93084,"like":207,"dislike":1,"score":206,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:30:52.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫佢地改埋名同埋換埋家人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47eb17871cbd0a15024588dfc66631e58bdd8a2e","tid":1758561,"uid":24634,"like":133,"dislike":1,"score":132,"quote":{"pid":"9cd87626ed1002f2073143cdc364b